🐕 Welcome to Shibe OS!

You are now running Shibe OS, your secure dental office portal!

This system is running in a *read-only, bootable container* for maximum security and stability.

✅ You can install apps via Flatpak (example: flatpak install flathub org.mozilla.firefox)
✅ You can layer system packages via rpm-ostree (example: rpm-ostree install libreoffice)
✅ Your user files, downloads, and documents are fully writable and normal.

System updates are managed cleanly through container upgrades.
To update your OS, just run:

  sudo bootc upgrade

and reboot when prompted.

For help, contact your Shibe OS administrator 🐕🦷
